  "summary": "Binary columnar storage optimized for TPC-H analytical workload. Large fact tables (lineitem 60M, orders 15M) sorted by frequently-filtered date columns (l_shipdate, o_orderdate) with zone maps for range pruning. Low-cardinality string columns (l_returnflag, l_linestatus, c_mktsegment, o_orderstatus) dictionary-encoded as uint8_t. Composite indexes: sorted on primary keys (join probes), hash on foreign keys and GROUP BY columns. Delta encoding on sorted date columns. 256K row blocks enable L3-cache-friendly parallel processing across 64 cores with per-block zone map skipping."
